Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Lakeside Cottage",
  "city": "Austin",
  "monthly_rent": 2200,
  "bedrooms": 3
}

### Create property #3
POST http://localhost:3000/properties
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Downtown Loft",
  "city": "Dallas",
  "monthly_rent": 1800,
